{"title":"Git remove and add remote repository","slug":"2018/02/remove-and-add-remote-repository","date":"2018-02-06T03:42:34.000Z","updated":"2024-04-03T06:02:32.390Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/2018/02/remove-and-add-remote-repository.json","excerpt":null,"covers":null,"content":"<p>如果是通过 https 方式来 pull 和 push 代码，每次都要输入烦人的账号和密码<br>可以通过切成成 ssh 方式：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 取消远程仓库</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">git remote remove origin</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 关联远程仓库</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">git remote add origin git@github.com:shenxianpeng/blog.git</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n","more":"<p>如果是通过 https 方式来 pull 和 push 代码，每次都要输入烦人的账号和密码<br>可以通过切成成 ssh 方式：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 取消远程仓库</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">git remote remove origin</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 关联远程仓库</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">git remote add origin git@github.com:shenxianpeng/blog.git</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n","categories":[{"name":"Git","path":"api/categories/Git.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Git","path":"api/tags/Git.json"}]}